{
  "stem": "16503.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 330.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we got to Prague, he gave me the money, and there was, there was furniture in our apartment, which was partially ours still because the Germans were in it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we went into the apartment, got into the bathtub, scrubbed ourselves, looked like-- I don't know if you know the famous name of a Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was terrible-- just terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister-- I put her to bed, and I got in touch with the United Restitution.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was United Restitution in Prague or something Jewish something, Congress or-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was an American-funded fund.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, they came, and they got my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she went right into hospital, where she stayed for six months in a very touch-and-go situation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she recovered, and she got well, and touch wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She's fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She got married two years later, and now she's going to be celebrating her 50th anniversary with her husband in Haifa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she's got two sons-- healthy sons, very successful-- in Israel and a handful of grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she is a very satisfied Israeli.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Though she wasn't, wasn't a Zionist, her husband was, and therefore, that's how her story is finished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Funny.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to say, well, the [NON-ENGLISH], which was our second name, girls, they got back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's about all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- even my uncle, which was a [? straight ?] brother-- younger brother-- of my father, but he had a mixed marriage, so he finished only for a few months in, in Theresienstadt-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was so scared that we-- that the world will dump us on him that he was absolutely awful.",
      "word_count": 56
    }
  ],
